## Metadata
mod-title = Mod Content Manager

modcontent-installprompt =
    OpenKrush requires artwork and audio from the original game.

    Quick Install will automatically download the freeware Multiplayer Demo content.

    Advanced Install includes options for copying the music, videos, and other content from an original KKnD disc or digital installation.
modcontent-header =
    Game content may be extracted from the original game discs or an existing digital install. OpenKrush can also download the base game files from an online mirror of the KKnD Xtreme Multiplayer Demo.

